citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T05:07:13.000Z","msg":"我之前是在麥當勞打工的，而我產薯條的原則是：<br />\n「幹你娘塞爆」<br />\n沒錯，就是幹你娘塞爆，老子才不管甚麼公司虧損三小的，每次產的薯條就是姬芭一大包。小薯產成大薯，中薯產成巨薯。大薯買一送一，跟把整個薯條站的薯條全送給你沒兩樣。<br />\n<br />\n我還記得，我那個月上班25天，經理跑來跟我說，這個月薯條虧損二十六箱，你有頭緒嗎？<br />\n<br />\n我他媽的怎麼會知道。"},{"pid":"d7cedc218b9b5d786a537bfd44a37c105b6312dc","tid":1001264,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f8b7f0055c02516973c19003ff269368b926ce7","tid":1001264,"uid":46195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T04:58:24.000Z","msg":"唔係個個ratio乘落去都係109.8<br />\n應該跟邊個 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T05:08:13.000Z","msg":"跟數字大啲嗰個<br />\n感覺誤差細啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b1fadd411ba9ce9f253870bbbd96b5743806fd1","tid":1001264,"uid":209663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2092903edc11fa755f9803d53e07639c642bd92","tid":1001264,"uid":62815,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T04:50:09.000Z","msg":"你應該告學校<br />\n告香港嘅教育制度<br />\n竟然咁多年都無發現你要特殊教育"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T05:36:07.000Z","msg":"同朕check下條傻佬做心弓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"567e21db96ad73724658bb3999daf9b90d2161a0","tid":1001264,"uid":209663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b1fadd411ba9ce9f253870bbbd96b5743806fd1","tid":1001264,"uid":209663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2092903edc11fa755f9803d53e07639c642bd92","tid":1001264,"uid":62815,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T04:50:09.000Z","msg":"你應該告學校<br />\n告香港嘅教育制度<br />\n竟然咁多年都無發現你要特殊教育"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T05:36:07.000Z","msg":"同朕check下條傻佬做心弓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T05:36:25.000Z","msg":"做乜*"},{"pid":"d2acf18ebd2030b65283a3cee8a0b981b6d9d023","tid":1001264,"uid":209663,"like":0,"dislike":0,